stock participation plan
under this plan, eligible employees may purchase shares of intel's common stock at 85% of fair market value at specific, predetermined dates. approximately 80% of
the company's employees were participating in the plan as of december28, 2002. of the 944million shares authorized to be issued under the plan, 109.7million shares remained
available for issuance at december28, 2002. employees purchased 17.0million shares in 2002 (13.0million in 2001 and 8.9million in 2000) for $338million
($351million in 2001 and $305million in 2000).
